# Run a quick test that will perform 30 rps per second during 10 seconds:
# artillery quick -q --duration 10 --rate 30 -o /Users/ssf/Project-mac/AWS/benchmark/output.json  https://(...).execute-api.ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/test/py-hello